Jambudipa is the apple rose country, and that's what India was called at that time, Jambudipa, the apple rose country.

30
00:03:16,899 --> 00:03:21,002
Now, I'll just read the next one because the next one just balances this.

31
00:03:21,021 --> 00:03:24,645
Monks, this samsara is without discoverable beginning.

32
00:03:25,105 --> 00:03:32,152
The first point is not discerned of beings roaming and wandering on, hindered by ignorance and fettered by craving.

33
