71
00:08:14,495 --> 00:08:16,338
And that's where the attachment comes.

72
00:08:17,262 --> 00:08:18,384
And that's where the suffering comes.

73
00:08:19,507 --> 00:08:23,516
Then he says of course that it's enough to become disenchanted.

74
