00:10:50,639 --> 00:10:55,966
Just something that sustains and gives everybody enough food, enough clothing, etc.

93
00:10:56,405 --> 00:10:57,326
It's always really growth.

94
00:10:59,110 --> 00:11:02,833
And it's just very much a western thing.

95
00:11:03,654 --> 00:11:05,937
Very much a western thing.

