174
00:20:09,292 --> 00:20:26,490
observing, observing thoughts, observing images, feeling and observing sensations and feelings within our bodies, we're actually moving back into that primordial state of pure intuitive awareness.

175
00:20:28,972 --> 00:20:33,336
That's why the Buddha says those who are mindful are in the presence of Nibbāna.

